\c 126
\s Ukubonga iN\nd kosi\nd* ngokubuyisela kwayo abathunjiweyo eZiyoni
\d Ingoma yokwenyuka
\p
\v 1 Lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* ibuyisa abathunjiweyo beZiyoni\x + Jobe 42.10.\x*, saba njengabaphuphayo\x + Seb. 12.9.\x*.
\v 2 Umlomo wethu wasugcwala uhleko, lolimi lwethu ukuhlabelela\x + Jobe 8.21.\x*. Basebesithi phakathi kwezizwe: IN\nd kosi\nd* ibenzele izinto ezinkulu\x + Luka 1.49. 1 Sam. 12.24. Hlab. 71.19. Neh. 6.16.\x*.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* isenzele izinto ezinkulu; siyathokoza.
\p
\v 4 Buyisa, N\nd kosi\nd*, ukuthunjwa kwethu, njengezifula\x + Jobe 6.15.\x* zeningizimu\x + Hlu. 1.15.\x*.
\v 5 Abahlanyela ngezinyembezi bazavuna ngentokozo\x + Jer. 31.9.\x*.
\v 6 Yena ohamba ahambe ekhala inyembezi, ephethe inhlanyelo yokuhlanyela, isibili uzabuya ethokoza, ethwele inyanda zakhe\x + Jobe 28.18.\x*.
